TopicTitle: ModuleManager cannot parse ratedBurnTime in TestFlight, resulting in errors

Articles.Content:
Line 266, Module TestFlightReliability_Engine Cycle.

bt15 and btPlus are supposed to be set to the rated burn time.

Yet MM could not parse this variable, while it obviously could with every other variable with the same format.

https://drive.google.com/file/d/1M1vG9pzdl381N_SrAgHXM7Zf3PAKL5xm/view?usp=sharing (MMPatch.log)

For testing, please use this file:

https://drive.google.com/file/d/1zkib0Gv3kJhUlmcCayKI3IROrw1CmXRU/view?usp=sharing and paste it into GameData. Requires TestFlight and MM.
